						               													<description>ICE CREAM YOU SCREAM! is a family game for all ages where you each own a competing ice cream shop. You roll 7 dice to dish out ice cream cones complete with whipped cream and a cherry on top. Players roll up to seven dice per turn trying to build their treat with a flavored cone, cherry, whipped cream, and 1-4 specific scoops to score points. As long as one die on your roll can build onto the cone you've started, you can keep rolling to complete it or risk your progress to add more scoops and freeze out your opponents. Push your luck too far and you'll end up with brain freeze and find your chances of victory dropping precipitously.&amp;#10;Once one player has sold cones of all four flavors, whoever has sold the most total scoops wins!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
